	<description><![CDATA[
				<div style="max-width: 550px;">The Tech Space app is built to work smoothly with <a href="https://yootheme.com/page-builder" target="_blank">YOOtheme Pro</a>. This app does not include any templates and needs to be templated with the YOOtheme Pro page builder. It inherits the content structure from the <a href="https://yootheme.com/joomla-templates/tech-space" target="_blank">Tech Space theme package</a>. Its layouts and styles can be found in the YOOtheme Pro libraries.</div>
